Comment: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:29.16,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,{ENG}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:29.16,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,Your instincts start to go crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:32.42,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,like a cornered mouse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:35.61,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,now, standing in an abyss of despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:38.87,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,you jumped into the railway crossing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.02,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you’re my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:45.14,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,so take my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:48.34,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you’re alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:51.63,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,you've got nowhere to go, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:54.57,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,But with things like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:58.44,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,we’re able to love each other
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:00:59.88,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,It repeats again;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:02.86,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,A flashback, the buzzing cicadas...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:06.05,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,And you, who will never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:09.26,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,Our matching keychains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:12.42,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,are being torn apart for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.45,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,The girl with her pale white skin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:18.83,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,that the summer got rid of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:25.65,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,I find myself wanting to be possessed by her so much it brings me to tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:41.26,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,My true nature starts to break loose
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:42.98,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,at the start of September,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:44.36,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,marked by the ringing of chimes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:47.55,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,a flower vase placed on the next target,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:50.67,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,and the one who started it... was me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:53.95,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,It’s true, you’re to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:57.13,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,just look at me and me only
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:02:00.35,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,It’s true, you want someone to help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:03.62,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:06.57,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,I gently place a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:10.02,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,on your drowning hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:14.61,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,Those faintly smiling beasts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:18.00,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,dig their nails into you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:21.39,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,until their hearts are refreshed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:24.45,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,and now your skirt is uneven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:30.77,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,A scream that seemed as though it cut off the silence of summer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:37.73,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,echos through the classroom, in the window is the blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:03:07.97,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,Of course, you're my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:11.15,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,so take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:14.37,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,Of course, you’re gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:17.59,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,and I’ve got nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:20.44,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,If we were able to love each other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:23.37,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,in that transparent world~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:27.70,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,It repeats again;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.64,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,A flashback, the buzzing cicadas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:34.02,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,And you, who will never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.23,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,Our matching keychains
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:40.45,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,are being torn apart for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:43.46,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,The girl with that pale white skin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:46.75,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,that the summer got rid of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:53.01,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,I find myself wanting to be possessed by her so much it makes me sad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.78,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,You were just transparent,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:04:00.05,DefaultEng,,0,0,0,,and pointed at me
